						               													<description>Between a Rock and a Hard Place&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In 1944 the USMC 1st Division was tasked to attack and secure the island fortress of Pelieu.  The small island had become such a rabbit warren of honeycombed defenses that the USMC spent weeks grinding away at, taking the division close to complete exhaustion as a combat formation.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This scenario booklet looks at the part of that battle, presenting a a scenario for the rules A Leader of Men by TFP Games.  &amp;#10;The scenario put you in control of either USMC or Japanese forces.  &amp;#10;It may also be used as a solo play scenario using the rules in the ALoM rule book.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This scenario is not for the faint of heart, it will require courage and resolution to make it, and sometimes an acceptance that today you may have failed.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This scenario contains:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     a deployment map, &amp;#10;     scenario orders of battle and &amp;#10;     special rules.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
